<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.1/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="your-custom-styles.css">
    <title>Rekonnect Alumni Association</title>
</head>
<body>

<section class="about-us-section py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Discover the Rekonnect Experience</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <img src="images/about.jpg" alt="Our University" class="img-fluid mb-3">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h3>Building Connections, Fostering Growth</h3>
                <p>Welcome to Rekonnect Alumni Association, where a community of like-minded alumni comes together to nurture connections and shared growth. We are dedicated to fostering your success and celebrating your journey within our vibrant community.</p>
                <p>Embark on the Rekonnect experience and join a network that values lifelong connections and supports your ongoing success.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center mt-5">
            <h3>Our Mission</h3>
            <p>At Rekonnect, our mission is to create lasting networking opportunities for our alumni, connecting them with peers and resources essential for success in the competitive job market. Today, you have the opportunity to experience our network and explore its countless resources.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="row mt-4">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <h3>Meet the Visionaries Behind Rekonnect</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="team-members d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-center">
                    <div class="team-member col-md-3">
                        <img src="/images/1.jpg" alt="President" class="img-fluid max-width-500">
                        <div class="member-info">
                            <h4>Mikael Lane</h4>
                            <p><strong>[2007 Computing Alumni]</strong> Founder and Strategist at Rekonnect</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="team-member col-md-3">
                        <img src="/images/2.avif" alt="Vice President" class="img-fluid max-width-500">
                        <div class="member-info">
                            <h4>Lee Yuna</h4>
                            <p><strong>[2010 Engineering Alumni]</strong> Event Manager at Rekonnect</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="team-member col-md-3">
                        <img src="/images/3.jpg" alt="Treasurer" class="img-fluid max-width-500">
                        <div class="member-info">
                            <h4>Nadia Tyla</h4>
                            <p><strong>[2021 Business Alumni]</strong> Finance Manager at Rekonnect</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mt-5">
            <h3>Our Aspirations and Goals</h3>
            <p>Looking ahead, Rekonnect aims to broaden our impact, fortify our network, and deliver even greater value to our esteemed alumni. We are dedicated to upholding the university's vision of nurturing leaders prepared to confront the challenges of tomorrow.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

</body>
</html>
